window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Spacer, Smuggler, Pirate, Spy: Publisher's Pack</i> contains Books 1 and 2 of the Spacer, Smuggler, Pirate, Spy series.</p> <p><b><i>Spacer</i></b><b>, Book 1:</b></p> <p>Jon Bartlett's path is clear before him: finish his last year of schooling, then off on the family's ships to learn the intricacies of interstellar trade. But a message of tragedy at home comes for him, and his expected life is flung far out of reach and he's cast into a role he never wanted.</p> <p><b><i>Smuggler</i></b><b>, Book 2:</b></p> <p>There are “nice” jobs that come my way, and there are profitable jobs that come my way. Now, these things do, on occasion, come along inside each other's orbits - but it's more of a cometary sort of thing, if you take my meaning.</p> <p>Avrel Dansby is troubled.</p>"; 
